  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ECHO Burkina Nutrition Top-Up 2018</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to provide food and nutrition assistance to conflict-affected households and people in greatest vulnerability in the Sahel and North Central regions of Burkina Faso. 
This humanitarian support will go to 3200 households of Internal Displaced People (IDPs) and 1400 host families affected by terrorist threats in Sahel Region in Burkina Faso. CA shares 50% of targeted people.</narrative>
  </description>
